  "title": "Senior Accounts Executive",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><p>1. Reviewing of accounting entries.</p><p>3. Preparation and passing of accounting entries.</p><p>4. Bank and cash reconciliations.</p><p>5. Preparation of accounting schedules and fixed assets.</p><p>6. Preparation of unaudited financial statements.</p><p>7. Payment and payroll processing.</p><p>8. GST submission.</p><p>9. CPF submission.</p><p>10. IR8A submission.</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><p>1. Degree/Diploma in Accountancy (or ACCA/LCCI equivalent).</p><p>2. Applicants with prior working experience preferred.</p><p>3. Able to work independently and as a team.</p><p>4. Have good command of Microsoft Office and Xero Cloud Accounting Software.</p><p>5. To start immediately.<br /><br />6. Good communication skills.</p>",
